<speak version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US">
  <voice name="en-US-Adam:DragonHDLatestNeural">
    Enterprises already have identity systems and governance.
    <break time="650ms"/>
    Genesis Mesh does not replace local authority.
    <break time="350ms"/>
    It lets organizations recognize external trust while keeping their own policy and revocation decisions.
    <break time="650ms"/>
    That is the difference between integration and centralization.
  </voice>
</speak>
